# proto-file: protowire/schema/v1/descriptor.proto
# proto-message: protowire.schema.v1.AnnotationList
#
# Golden lowered annotation carrier (RFC-001 §8.1) covering all three
# Literal variants (issue #64):
#   - a linker-RESOLVED enum-value reference (EnumLiteral),
#   - a typed message literal (google.protobuf.Any, serialized at
#     lowering; here fixtures.literals.Money{currency: "USD", units: 5},
#     whose wire bytes are "\n\003USD\020\005"),
#   - a homogeneous list literal (LiteralValue elements — values, not
#     arguments: no names, no expressions).
# Cross-port conformance: lowering the use sites in 10_literal_args.proto
# (all three source forms, per the §5.1 literal grammar / issue #102)
# must produce a semantically equal carrier.

entries {
  name: "fixtures.literals.sample"
  args {
    name: "value"
    literal {
      enum_value {
        enum_type: "fixtures.literals.OrderStatus"
        value_name: "CANCELLED"
        number: 3
      }
    }
  }
  location { file: "fixtures/literals.proto" line: 49 column: 5 }
}
